column1: Table of the L. fabarum wasps sampled for the study
Samples that could not successfuly establish in the lab were not used for experiements and therefore are omitted from this table
sample_id: unique identifier for each Lysiphlebus fabarum clonal line
site: general name covering multiple samples from the same location (roughly 200m diameter circle)
plant_species: host plant from which the sample was collected
aphid_species: name of the host species the sample was collected from
genotype: arbitrary number given to each unique genotype, determined with the microsatellite analysis
niche: was the genotype found in more than one host species?
